Description: Handle of Knidian pottery transport amphora. Rectangular stamp
Curator's comments: Only known from Petrie's drawing in his Journal, 1884-5, p.122, 18. Names, Asklepiodoros, Euphron. Not the same piece as BM 1955,0920.107.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (JB.0319)
